columns_description:
Current status of the facility: 
Active - Currently regulated under one of the Bulk Storage Programs;  
Unregulated/Closed - A facility that does not meet the thresholds for quantity or product type for regulation under one of the Bulk Storage Programs or has been closed by the DEC for management purposes.  For example, to eliminate duplicate facilities;  
Unregistered - A facility that is not currently registered but meets the requirements for regulation under one of the Bulk Storage Programs; a PBS regulated facility located in a delegated county*; or a facility which is not regulated which submitted a Bulk Storage registration application which was returned unprocessed;
Inactive– Facility is not operating (verified by inspection or other reliable means) but closure not completed/verified.
